title: Spoons - Collectible Spoons
description:
Spoons were an awesome Canadian 80s new wave/new romantic band. Gordon Deppe (vocals, guitar), Sandy Horne (vocals, bass), Rob Preuss (keyboards, piano, 1980-?), Derrick Ross (drums), Brett Wickens (keyboards, piano, 1979-1980). Deppe and Horne (the only constant members of the band) were high school sweethearts. Don't miss out on this great CD!  CD rip - 320 K
